dad de vida en personas con\\Nenfermedades serias y/o de riesgo vital, al igual que sus familias.","guid":"axmLhAKaZ7cBQOhG2cmFWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Dolor","guid":"nVgtfgZtDQ4HWZaje9cReQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Definición ","guid":"OYV4E1TygSDkgDxrJLr4Pw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Es una experiencia sensorial o emocional desagradable,\\Nasociada a daño tisular real o potencial.","guid":"9NfRhFLeCK_oF4pt7VUZ2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Manejo del dolor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Paso 1 - Dolor leve a moderado \\NAINES c/s coadyuvante","guid":"anhy1zRP4azWIBCmj0qjAg","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Manejo\\Nde base","guid":"rKXO_UJvfCkIWmuH9_T_Cg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Paracetamol","guid":"vAh0WFDV_UJpgjEtk-O6ow","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Dosis mínima y máxima","guid":"fKYpejCUPIuVmAFcoZANaQ","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"500 - 1.000 mg. C/ 6 hrs.","guid":"u-SoVWvbtx-2WHiU6FcmuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Potencia analgésica","guid":"5tVQi1xcFwlAkxWUvcaCAw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Similar al ácido acetilsalicílico.","guid":"fckLsF3bUH22KAsuS2Gpnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"Toxicidad hepática","guid":"CDSGZ1ZidUHGaaJn-ckgIA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"dosis dependiente","guid":"j_Sn_-a4I7ZU-MtFmcpH0Q","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"habitualmente con dosis de 140 mg/kg","guid":"x9DQxcovDPRudB5CvfFZuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"En insuficiencia hepática la dosis de toxicidad es de 2000 mg /24 hrs.","guid":"G7UDP0v0g0VN7xfCqkw9yw","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"24","text":"Reacciones adversas\\Nmás comunes","guid":"GZdvfcfv2XaLARqJ-NyQOw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Desorientación, mareos,\\Nnefritis intersticial","guid":"EQZY-JzWFxwUSr_OrfoVrA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"23","text":"Metalizol","guid":"o_0kRK9iVdEZfwfBdaSKMg","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Dosis mínima","guid":"BUThEeYttXxcl1ZqINlgbQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"300 - 600 mg. C/ 6 hrs.","guid":"cev7UOnZB-QGpVbPweZLFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"Dosis máxima","guid":"drpPHlJDNQDLnRd4iJicAg","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Dosis máxima 8000 mg / 24 hrs.","guid":"nF985yeHYrMxlu5wQ-b3FA","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"Consideraciones ","guid":"lz9w9cBO-ToAuoDYaWVcfA","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Por su actividad antiespasmódica es útil en los dolores viscerales.","guid":"jxfjBOZQvjNBRLFG-gaM1w","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Preguntar sobre alergia específica al principio activo.","guid":"fo9Ze4t_zJy74917U4Auxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"35","text":"Reacciones\\Nadversas","guid":"5j-WBdPffbIOC22n_fG8Ug","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Más comunes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Toxicidad renal y agresión a la mucosa gástrica.","guid":"vqa0yYyKvhqd5RLKJhHc-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Rara vez anemia hemolítica, agranulocitosis.","guid":"eW0lT3WIH_KST2o_0XsiHA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"22","text":"Alternativas ","guid":"9EvTnX2b6mhniDvJ2QMw7A","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Inuprofeno ","guid":"x5aCAIbLIDZYNCwBYy4m3A","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Indometacina ","guid":"S0mwjA_DQnUXXux8o4SSDg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Dicofenaco sódico ","guid":"drT8kiw0IpE4k4_xIZbdsw","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"Ketoprofeno","guid":"55l4_lfbMPaNadsgzaCqjA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"Ketorolaco","guid":"a_N5AdZl1sMh-w1d0Wgo1g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"21","text":"Paso 2 - Dolor persistente o moderado a severo del principio\\NAINES + Opioide débil c/s coadyuvante","guid":"GoaIHcPUHNE0SdmOIYsiHQ","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Manejo\\Nde base","guid":"Lc99P1vUVgfmo6P9Y-cChg","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Codeína","guid":"bqhR2h0ilx96mJv9vsIgJw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Tramadol de\\Nacción rápida","guid":"h6LEvrjed1ZjcmoXkbgJ6Q","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Dosis","guid":"hOnYKD3fMrG3wtZMMyMutw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Via oral Gotas o comprimidos de acción rápida 50 -\\N100 mg C/ 6 hrs. Dosis máxima 400 mg / 24 hrs.","guid":"zWXN_DXimyOvB79Sg7tnLg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Comprimidos orales 37,5 mg tramadol asociados a 375 mg\\Nde paracetamol C/ 12 horas oral de liberación sostenida.","guid":"WEzMI1ST3ARbs0TSAIlRiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Consideraciones","guid":"JCbPVDRw2dLp3eeYHxIBUQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Una vez conseguido el control del dolor es aconsejable utilizar las\\Npresentaciones de liberación retardada, que son equipotentes.","guid":"Vg8wr78w_rEuifcRrl5qnQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Potencia analgésica","guid":"D-CGOeoI3iAOeMWSWwQFRg","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Ligeramente superior a la de la codeina\\N(100 mg equivalen a 120 mg de codeina).","guid":"-lI1z_Z3jZpff-n16fQXEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"Respecto de morfina oral potencia analgésica","guid":"0FR9eidIjmpgxBxUQLJL8g","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"10 mg de tramadol oral equivalen\\Na 2 mg de morfina oral.","guid":"8gA9EymG2ivi3AKaoKzTHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"56","text":"Reacciones\\Nadversas","guid":"2Y-XUmGidUue7id5wFd-xQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Estreñimiento, menos frecuente que con la codeína, prevenir con vaselina liquida.\\NEl resto de efectos secundarios son similares a los de la codeina.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"53","text":"Alternativas","guid":"bOT5OE8osTUXqPPvEZ5noA","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Tranadol de acción sostenida","guid":"93OhsBvAXIWbROfdjfQJug","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"Oxiácido a de liberación controlada","guid":"D1eAkcflkYWHrG59LFY2FQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"21","text":"Paso 3 - Dolor persistente o severo desde el principio\\NAINES + Opioide fuerte c/s coadyuvante","guid":"vx2swZ0Z0VFc-NpmafhMfw","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Manejo\\Nde base","guid":"WEM3RG4te4pDf2YHB0ZNjg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Morfina de acción rápida","guid":"bk96_PTarcUh6luCU5nkjg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Metadona","guid":"c5AwKkLITajHt0BY2WEkFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"Alternativas","guid":"2EJBqYThVpnkj2Y93mp8BQ","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Morfina de acción sostenida.","guid":"QsZ5yIg6SldQqLDPUmQjbg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Oxicodona de liberación controlada","guid":"60jULMLF0KULxm4hMfXe_Q","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Parches de\\NFentanilo","guid":"-2RDRLqsbxKzGJQLxvrCuw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"25-50 mg/ 72 horas parche transdérmico","guid":"DOs1I8d_2xh-8LSdBHXyxA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Consideraciones ","guid":"ax-sy0ADVIZjyFbGIW3XIw","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"No fraccionar.","guid":"aJcNXBWyA3_TJFtNn4904g","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"No tiene techo analgésico.","guid":"l1_-Lx9DH-vRz5KypzwK1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"Reacciones\\Nadversas","guid":"PYTvB7gsUMM3VswnvMUuJQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Produce menos estreñimiento, sedación y\\Ndeterioro cognitivo que la morfina.","guid":"MNCvI_6afQXyrXDttzTuWw","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Las nauseas son ligeramente más\\Nfrecuentes con fentanilo que con morfina.","guid":"hViBuqqP2ZUC7UuyDqy6uw","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"En la piel puede producir eritema y prurito.","guid":"pFosxeRNYoj8nlLUJOXuWw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"Debido a la farmacocinética del fentanilo parche, los efectos\\Nsecundarios pueden persistir varias horas tras la retirada del parche.","guid":"iq9p_f6zrcqTwEtXM8EErg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"75","text":"Parche de\\Nbuprenorfina","guid":"nfRtlv9pSK93jVj6UATSag","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"1C/ 72 hrs parche transdérmico (35 / 52,5/ 70 ug/h) ativos","guid":"GbvQTFNtsG3Ow9eRqZUyHQ","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"Consideraciones ","guid":"cvIsriDT8f-DZTIbkdXjPA","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Se puede fraccionar","guid":"2oLYBTHxJHETWEjXgsntUg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"No tiene techo analgésico","guid":"p1tA6z5PeOTnb9XblGYb0w","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Utilizar con precaución en:\\Nancianos, caquécticos o febriles.","guid":"rPitpnHL3336Ls-sEBFWjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"88","text":"Reacciones\\Nadversas","guid":"rJ91Af2OPvX0JkoKP7tP3g","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Puede producir nauseas,\\Nvomitos, somnolencia.","guid":"pQWmNkm5qyzFWkOZ58AogA","children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"18","text":"Manejo RAM\\Nopioides","guid":"OKIS1uBPb_XW_9PA9buORA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Náuseas y vómitos\\N80%","guid":"Mbu7s2BaQXYtvLcELxxvhg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Prevención ","guid":"zOenoDi7LC60k0SKXOY6mw","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Alimentación e hidratación fraccionada y frecuente.","guid":"Aqnh3XzbEB1hxrLPOPcVaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Manejo ","guid":"Ko9Kpqd-vrocw8s7SeAW8A","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Metoclopramida 10 mg CMP, gotas; 30 minutos\\Nantes del desayuno, almuerzo y comida.","guid":"ozD80l_kIYFIJIk1BWVfMg","children":[]},{"id"